            "tooltip": {
              "expr": {
                "Literal": {
                  "Value": "'The map shows the balance between emissions and emissions avoided through the implementation of a biorefinery in each municipality in mainland Portugal, according to the selections made in the filters for municipality, CHP and Practice. The redder the municipality is coloured, the more emissions it produces, and the bluer it is, the greater the potential for capturing emissions through the biorefinery. It is possible to filter a specific municipality by selecting its geographical boundary on the map. If you then wish to select a municipality in the respective filter, you must click on an area of the map outside the geographical boundary of mainland Portugal in order to clear the selection made on the map.'"
                }
